            "title": "滬指開市跌6點 深成指跌9點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地股市初段偏軟，上證綜指以3348點開市，跌6點或0.2%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指開市報10781點，亦跌9點或0.09%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數跌4點或0.12%，開報3942點；創業板指數開市報2223點，跌3點或0.14%。</p>\n</div>",
